# Greek and Roman [[god]] of the [[underworld]].
# The brightest and first known [[Kuiper belt object]], originally considered the ninth [[planet]] but now classified as a [[dwarf planet]], represented by the symbol {{Unicode|[[♇]]}} in astronomy and [[Image:Pluto's astrological symbol.svg|16px]] in astrology.

